						               													<description>Fire and Move is a game about &amp;ldquo;tanks&amp;rdquo; &amp;ndash; it&amp;rsquo;s that simple. It&amp;rsquo;s fun to play and easy to set up with uncomplicated systems. This game is fast and involves everyone.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;To us, Rules for Playing Battles are aimed at players, this means that all players should be involved throughout the game. The action should be continuous for all players and everyone should have the chance to win. Just because you have the best tank, with the best armour and a bigger gun, you shouldn&amp;rsquo;t automatically win.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;We chose to focus on the things that can happen quickly in combat and by speeding these elements up we moved the game along at pace. The concept for this game is to play the game in quite small areas (12 x 12 hexes) and be quick to play.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;It is about Troops and Platoons of tanks working together in games with Companies and Platoons, Squadrons or Troops.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Game Inventory:&amp;#10;Map Notes&amp;#10;Tank Table&amp;#10;Playsheet&amp;#10;Scenario &amp;#10;16 page rules booklet&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Printed and downloadable versions available.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;-description from publisher's website&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
